WEBVTT

00:00:04.870 --> 00:00:06.320
Shah Rukh Khan: Mom. 
M-O-M, Mom.

00:00:06.320 --> 00:00:09.190
For our next speaker 
this word has two meanings.

00:00:09.190 --> 00:00:11.950
not just because she is a mother 
to two lovely children,

00:00:11.950 --> 00:00:14.970
also because she is deputy operations
director of MOM,

00:00:14.970 --> 00:00:17.200
which is an acronym 
for Mars Orbit Mission.

00:00:17.200 --> 00:00:22.660
She played a critical role in sending 
India millions of kilometres into space

00:00:22.660 --> 00:00:25.420
and landing on Mars
through the Mangalyan mission.

00:00:25.420 --> 00:00:28.510
(Applause)

00:00:28.710 --> 00:00:32.680
This scientist from 
Indian Space Research Organisation